      <title>普京访朝后朝鲜试射弹道导弹展示武力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-in-a-show-of-force-after-putin-s-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜发射一枚疑似弹道导弹，但似乎在飞行中失败，这是朝鲜试图展示武力的举动，大约一周前，朝鲜与俄罗斯达成军事协议，引起美国及其盟友的震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-in-a-show-of-force-after-putin-s-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 21:41:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
